  <h3>Conclusions</h3>

  <p class="text-field">
    Our analysis shows that there are some potentially problematic roads in Helsinki; especially Knutersintie has a very high accident-traffic volume ratio compared to other roads.
    It was a surprise that some major roads like Kehä 1, Hämeenlinnanväylä and Lahdenväylä have relative low accident-traffic volume ratios.
  </p>

